\i0\b0\fs24 \
\pard\pardeftab709\sa120

\f0 \cf0 10 kobolds stand watch here. Besides their swords and bows, they have torches, which they will throw into Room 22 to ignite the oil covering its floor. They will then attack any opponents not killed or driven away by the flames with their bows. Each kobold possesses 22 cp.
\f1 \
\pard\pardeftab709\sa120

